<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/8/uniqlo-u-2020-fall-winter-lookbook">优衣库发布 UNIQLO U 2020 秋冬系列 Lookbook</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359935" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/u.jpg" alt="" width="1560" height="1162" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/u.jpg 1560w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/u-360x268.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/u-768x572.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/u-1024x763.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1560px) 100vw, 1560px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，主打将高级时装元素融入日常单品的 Uniqlo U 系列正式更新 2020 年秋冬系列 Lookbook，其中包括 39 款男装、38 款女装和 4 款配件。</p>
<p>本季男装灵感来自数十年前欧洲青年街头文化，强调温暖质感；女装则以极简主义贯穿系列。系列将于 9 月上市。</p>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/2796439980/JgAMDlHEW?from=page_1006062796439980_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime">内衣品牌「内外」宣布王菲为全球代言人</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359937" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/water.jpg" alt="" width="1413" height="954" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/water.jpg 1413w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/water-360x243.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/water-768x519.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/water-1024x691.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1413px) 100vw, 1413px" /></p>
<p>昨天，国内专注于贴身衣物的生活方式品牌「NEIWAI 内外」宣布，王菲成为其品牌全球代言人，共同诠释「一切都好 自在内外」的全新品牌理念。</p>
<p>内外成立于 2012 年，除了网上旗舰店，内外在北上广深等 21 个城市设立了近 90 家线下品牌体验店。</p>
<h4><a href="http://news.mtime.com/2020/08/19/1603626.html">新版《尼罗河上的惨案》发布中字预告</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359938" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/213134.56029445_1000X1000.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/213134.56029445_1000X1000.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/213134.56029445_1000X1000-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/213134.56029445_1000X1000-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>时光网消息，肯尼思・布拉纳执导的新版《尼罗河上的惨案》发布中字预告片，影片将于 10 月 23 日在北美上映。</p>
<p><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=y3138h7ps5r" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p>故事改编自阿加莎名作，讲述了大侦探波洛在埃及度假期间，卷入到了一场危险的三角关系之中。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>东京本月超一百人中暑死亡</h4>
<p>日本已进入酷暑季节，多地最高气温高于人体体温，局部地区甚至超过 40 度。自 8 月以来，东京已有 103 人因中暑死亡，以老人为主。其中，80 多岁的有 42 人，70 多岁的 30 人，死者中有 84 人不用空调，占总数八成以上。还有 6 人在室外死亡。</p>
<p>网友：「一年比一年热。」「特别是室外工作者，很需要降温」「日本的电费太贵了，尤其是东京，很多老人家都不舍得用。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357582" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.archdaily.cn/cn/907727/uccasha-qiu-mei-zhu-guan-open-jian-zhu-shi-wu-suo">UCCA 沙丘美术馆 @ 秦皇岛·中国</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359874" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dune.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="616" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dune.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dune-360x222.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dune-768x473.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>今年，OPEN 建筑事务所设计的 UCCA 沙丘美术馆在有「博物馆界的奥斯卡」之称的文化地标先锋奖上获得亚太地区「年度新文化目的地奖」。</p>
<p>就如其名，美术馆坐落于海边的一片沙丘上，形态也如藏于沙丘之下的神秘洞穴。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359875" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/l.jpg" alt="" width="1074" height="1200" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/l.jpg 1074w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/l-360x402.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/l-768x858.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/l-916x1024.jpg 916w" sizes="(max-width: 1074px) 100vw, 1074px" /></p>
<p>在设计团队看来，将美术馆建在沙丘上，是对自然的敬畏，也是一种保护：因为沙丘美术馆的存在，这片沙丘将永远不会人为「被推平」，从而维护了千百年累积下来但也十分脆弱的沙丘生态系统。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359944" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/05_Gallery_by_WU_Qingshan.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="801" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/05_Gallery_by_WU_Qingshan.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/05_Gallery_by_WU_Qingshan-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/05_Gallery_by_WU_Qingshan-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/05_Gallery_by_WU_Qingshan-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>行走于美术馆内，在不同的时间，从不同的洞口眺望，大海都呈现出不一样的风景。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359876" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/07_Cafe_by_WU_Qingshan.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/07_Cafe_by_WU_Qingshan.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/07_Cafe_by_WU_Qingshan-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/07_Cafe_by_WU_Qingshan-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/07_Cafe_by_WU_Qingshan-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>